// CHALLENGE: uncomment the code below and see the car stats rendered import React from "react"; import ReactDOM from "react-dom"; import cars from "./practice" const [honda, tesla] = cars //Tesla Components const {coloursByPopularity: [teslaTopColor] , speedStats: teslaSpeed} = tesla const {topSpeed: teslaTopSpeed} = teslaSpeed //Honda Components const {coloursByPopularity: hondaColor, speedStats: hondaSpeed} = honda const [hondaTopColour] = hondaColor const {topSpeed: hondaTopSpeed} = hondaSpeed ReactDOM.render(
Brand Top Speed Top Color
{tesla.model} {teslaTopSpeed} {teslaTopColour}
{honda.model} {hondaTopSpeed} {hondaTopColour}
, document.getElementById("root") );
